{"tid":2514863,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Marvel最新影集《驚奇女士》片場照曝光！首位穆斯林超級英雄戰袍亮相","createTime":"2021-05-03T13:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T17:57:12.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"003a787b41f457771208a4f0827830b9d20c8e18","tid":2514863,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"漫威影集《驚奇女士》（Ms. Marvel）目前正在美國亞特蘭大拍攝，近來女主角伊曼維拉尼（Iman Vellani）換上如漫畫般的經典造型，現身街頭拍攝，扮相曝光後引起網友熱議。<br />\n<br />\n照片中，伊曼維拉尼戴著眼罩、披風，穿上以紅藍為主要色系的衣服，現場還有另一位主要演員瑞許沙哈（Rish Shah）。《驚奇女士》劇情描述巴基斯坦裔的美國16歲少女卡瑪拉克汗（Kamala Khan），相當崇拜「驚奇隊長」卡蘿丹佛斯，在碰觸到泰瑞根水晶產生的霧氣後獲得超能力，全身都能夠自由伸縮變形，更成為漫威首位穆斯林超級英雄。<br />\n<br />\n驚奇女士據傳未來會現身電影《驚奇隊長2》，先前公布選角時，執行製片之一的Sana Amanat便大讚18歲的伊曼維拉尼，「我們發現她時，就知道她是完美人選。」該劇也將顛覆超級英雄的影集風格，聚焦在青少年尋找自我、人際關係、家庭等方面。《驚奇女士》預計2021下半年於Disney +上線。"},{"pid":"cdff2a6d7f7186f13f0da7f258fa58a8184d81a4","tid":2514863,"uid":331739,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:50:06.000Z","msg":"第一位自爆英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27ba211c82d77a634f495139b22b5024ff57b97","tid":2514863,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T13:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQseMAMez2CBHNzwC3Uz9Z87CWjbDf8HstMbRyX1955X1?filename=5ucmXxU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ucmXxU.jpg&h=e5e26e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNwpyU9cPKpCscyXedNiwNBxfkDRR9tx1cuCF64vbsv91?filename=jsLDfjB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjsLDfjB.jpg&h=219edba1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcR3TkNX9xgY7QWMZXkV1GKFXa6HoheDwwiCwCU1s6CPR?filename=OchRAjD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOchRAjD.jpg&h=e